WEBVTT

00:00:00.703 --> 00:00:02.617
Let's face it:

00:00:02.617 --> 00:00:05.062
Driving is dangerous.

00:00:05.062 --> 00:00:08.160
It's one of the things that we don't like to think about,

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:11.812
but the fact that religious icons and good luck charms

00:00:11.812 --> 00:00:16.602
show up on dashboards around the world

00:00:16.602 --> 00:00:20.739
betrays the fact that we know this to be true.

00:00:20.739 --> 00:00:24.333
Car accidents are the leading cause of death

00:00:24.333 --> 00:00:28.503
in people ages 16 to 19 in the United States --

00:00:28.503 --> 00:00:31.346
leading cause of death --